data.description: Charming 3 bed and 2.5 bath townhouse that was recently updated in 2021 with newer roof, new appliances, flooring, and more. Sellers would love to stay, but are relocating for work. If you're looking for a community to go with this beautiful home, welcome to Kiln Creek. Enjoy resort style living at the pool, clubhouse, community park, playground, tennis court, basketball court, walking trail, or on the golf course. Central location with close proximity to shopping, dining, cultural attractions, etc. Please remove shoes or wear provided booties.
